description:
This module will be focused on some advanced topics which are not covered in basic polymer science. The topics include:

(1)    new polymerization methods (e.g. controlled radical polymerization, metallocene polymerization and olefin metathesis polymerization);

(2)    block copolymers and their applications;

(3)    dendritic macromolecules;

(4)    naturally occurring polymers and biopolymers;

(5)    inorganic and organometallic polymers;

(6)    supramolecular polymers and smart polymers;

(7)    conducting polymers and their applications
